metadata.name: Midnight : Miami Skyline
metadata.description:
1/1 Photographic images for my series "The Lonely Astronaut" taken during my trip to Art Basel in Miami, FL. The Lonely Astronaut is a photographic series that I started in 2017. I travel the world with a vintage high altitude suit taking photos in incredible places. You can read more about it

Here: https://www.thisiscolossal.com/2019/04/lonely-astronaut-series/

and

Here: https://www.nhpr.org/nh-news/2021-04-27/the-show-goes-on-photographer-brings-astronaut-series-to-manchester
